    dc:description "Figure 8. Ventrifurca phallaina sp. nov., male paratype (CIUQ- 020633), penis A dorsal view B lateral view C ventral view. Abbreviations: MS = macrosetae of penis; MS-A = proximal group of setae; MS-B ventroproximal group of setae; MS-C = distal group of setae; MS-D = dorso medial group of setae; MS-E = ventrodistal group of reduced setae, SC = stylar caps. Figures not scaled." ;
